/*React uses react virtual dom which updates the webpage instantly without fully reloading it 
JSX - jsx into javascript is done by babel
jsx - javascript inside html

RULES ABOUT JSX : 
 => cant return more than one html elemenet at once but we can wrap element in parent tag.
 
 eg : class Test extends React.compnent {
  render(){
    return {
      <div>
       <p>hello</p>
       <h1>hie</h1> 
      </div>
    };
  }
 }

 => use jsx inside for loops, if-else.

 eg : if(condition==true){
      return <p>kyu ni hori padhayi</p>
      } 
      else {
      return <h1>idhar dekho</h1>
      }

=> class becomes "className" in jsx.
=> html tags must be closed.*/

